For example, you fetched master to branch_a as your local develop branch, and then do
`git checkout branch_a`
you would on your local branch, and you can modfiy the code as you want, when you finished them
`git commit -a -m "modify code for test"`
finally you want to push this branch to you github branch, and before this you want to do rebase:
`git rebase master`
here, the master is the new code you fetched form carbon master.
At last, do
`git push YOUR_GITHUB_URL branch_a:YOUR_GITHUB_BRANCH`
